_coords": [[[1061.0, 870.0], [1095.0, 870.0], [1095.0, 1005.0], [1061.0, 1005.0]]], "lines": ["そっかー。"]}, {"box": [892, 903, 1031, 1065], "vertical": true, "font_size": 39, "lines_coords": [[[963.0, 903.0], [1031.0, 903.0], [1031.0, 1016.0], [963.0, 1016.0]], [[933.0, 915.0], [960.0, 915.0], [960.0, 1063.0], [933.0, 1063.0]], [[892.0, 916.0], [918.0, 916.0], [918.0, 1065.0], [892.0, 1065.0]]], "lines": ["西片も", "ひみつきち", "あったの？"]}, {"box": [157, 883, 393, 1108], "vertical": true, "font_size": 45, "lines_coords": [[[354.0, 883.0], [393.0, 883.0], [393.0, 1027.0], [354.0, 1027.0]], [[303.0, 885.0], [365.0, 885.0], [365.0, 975.0], [303.0, 975.0]], [[240.0, 915.0], [285.0, 915.0], [281.0, 1108.0], [236.0, 1108.0]], [[200.0, 918.0], [234.0, 918.0], [236.0, 1104.0], [202.0, 1104.0]], [[157.0, 916.0], [200.0, 916.0], [200.0, 1001.0], [157.0, 1001.0]]], "lines": ["あぁ、うん", "一応。", "小学校のころ", "友達と作った", "のが。"]}, {"box": [1087, 1475, 1166, 1601], "vertical": true, "font_size": 36, "lines_coords": [[[1127.0, 1475.0], [1166.0, 1475.0], [1166.0, 1575.0], [1127.0, 1575.0]], [[1087.0, 1477.0], [1121.0, 1477.0], [1121.0, 1601.0], [1087.0, 1601.0]]], "lines": ["どんな", "だった？"]}, {"box": [654, 1426, 733, 1610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 36, "lines_coords": [[[686.0, 1426.0], [733.0, 1426.0], [733.0, 1533.0], [686.0, 1533.0]], [[654.0, 1430.0], [680.0, 1430.0], [680.0, 1608.0], [654.0, 1608.0]]], "lines": ["いやー、", "よかったよ！！"]}, {"box": [230, 1468, 337, 1693], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[305.0, 1468.0], [337.0, 1468.0], [337.0, 1691.0], [305.0, 1691.0]], [[264.0, 1468.0], [296.0, 1468.0], [296.0, 1693.0], [264.0, 1693.0]], [[230.0, 1470.0], [256.0, 1470.0], [256.0, 1663.0], [230.0, 1663.0]]], "lines": ["ちっさかったけど", "ちゃんと葉っぱで", "屋根もあって．．．"]}], "img_path": "007.jpg"}, {"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "img_width": 1354, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [1123, 189, 1211, 303], "vertical": true, "font_size": 48, "lines_coords": [[[1162.0, 191.0], [1211.0, 191.0], [1211.